From: TrueNAS Community Sysexts <community-sysexts@truenas.org>
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] gasket: version guard for MODULE_IMPORT_NS quoting

Kernel >= 6.13 requires MODULE_IMPORT_NS argument to be a quoted string.
Older kernels use the unquoted form. Add a version guard with the
__has_include check for dma-buf.h retained.

---
 src/gasket_page_table.c | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/src/gasket_page_table.c b/src/gasket_page_table.c
index c9067cb..c1f04b4 100644
--- a/src/gasket_page_table.c
+++ b/src/gasket_page_table.c
@@ -54,8 +54,12 @@
 #include <linux/vmalloc.h>

 #if __has_include(<linux/dma-buf.h>)
+#if LINUX_VERSION_CODE >= KERNEL_VERSION(6, 13, 0)
+MODULE_IMPORT_NS("DMA_BUF");
+#else
 MODULE_IMPORT_NS(DMA_BUF);
 #endif
+#endif

 #include "gasket_constants.h"
 #include "gasket_core.h"
